Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:24.56,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Your very first princess summit. You must be over the moon, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:29.19,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, I am excited. But, to be honest, I'm a little nervous, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:30.35,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You're nervicited!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:33.79,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It's like you wanna jump up and down and yell "YAY ME!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:38.99,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,But you also wanna curl up in a teeny-tiny ball and hide at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.01,0:00:43.76,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We've all been there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.20,0:00:46.13,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm there almost every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:51.02,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You've got no reason to fret, Twi. Everything's gonna be just...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:51.95,Rarity,,0,0,0,,TWILIGHT!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:59.66,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Ugh, sorry darling, but I just realize you're not wearing your crown. You haven't forgotten it back in Ponyville, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:00.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's in my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:07.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Just feel a little self-conscious about wearing it. Haven't really gotten accustomed to these yet, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.76,0:01:13.91,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You are a princess now, Twilight. Embrace it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.48,0:01:19.88,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, if I had a crown like that, I would never take it off. Why, I'd sleep in the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:37.70,FlashSentry,,0,0,0,,Her highness, Princess Twilight Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.26,0:01:42.42,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Twilight! I haven't seen you since the coronation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.18,0:01:51.65,Celestia,,0,0,0,,We have so much to discuss. But, it can wait until tomorrow. You all look tired from your journey. Now, off to bed, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:10.20,Spike,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:13.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Spike. I'm just... worried, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:21.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadence was given the Crystal Empire to rule over. What if now that I'm a princess, Celestia expects me to lead a kingdom of my own?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:23.98,Spike,,0,0,0,,That would be awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:25.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No it would not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:29.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Just because I have this crown and these wings, it doesn't mean I'll be a good leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.05,0:02:36.39,Spike,,0,0,0,,Aw, sure you will, Twilight. Now come on, you should get some shut-eye. Big day tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:47.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Can't... tuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:53.41,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Just trying to get comfortable!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:40.75,Spike,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:46.93,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My crown! She's got my crown!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:50.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Stop! Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:54.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,She's stolen my crown!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:56.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:14.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What did you do with my crown?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:16.87,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Sorry it had to be this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:18.69,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,...Princess
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:23.10,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:32.37,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Sunset Shimmer. A former student of mine. She began her studies with me not long before Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:37.35,Celestia,,0,0,0,,But when she did not get what she wanted as quickly as she liked, she turned cruel and dishonest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:46.09,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I tried to help her. But she eventually decided to abandon her studies and pursue her own path, one that has sadly led to her stealing your crown
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:49.28,Spike,,0,0,0,,She replaced Twilight's with this one
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:58.73,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I suppose Sunset Shimmer thought you wouldn't notice right away that this was not yours. And by the time you did, it would be too late to go after your crown and element of harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:03.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But I don't understand! Where'd she go? Why did she take the crown?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:06.67,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You'll soon know more about this place than even I do
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:18.23,Luna,,0,0,0,,This is no ordinary mirror. It is a gateway to another world. A gateway that opens once every thirty moons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:20.09,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Sparkly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:28.32,Luna,,0,0,0,,It has always been kept in the throne room of Canterlot Castle. But when Princess Cadence took over the Crystal Empire, we sent it here for her to watch over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:35.18,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I had always hoped that Sunset Shimmer would someday use it to return. To come back to Equestria seeking my guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:38.22,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Obviously, this is not what has happened
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:51.64,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Twilight, you must use the mirror to go into this other world and retrieve your crown. Without it, the other elements of harmony have no power and Equestria is left without one of its most important means of defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:59.19,Luna,,0,0,0,,Your crown does not belong in the place Sunset Shimmer now calls home
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:09.44,Luna,,0,0,0,,And in her posession your element of harmony will no doubt be used to bring harm to the inhabitants of this other realm. They will not have the power to defend themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:13.80,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You understand the importance of your task?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:15.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:17.88,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Good. Then you must go at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:27.40,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,She's going? We're going with her! Right, girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:30.55,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I'm so nervicited!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:33.28,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You do realize that's not a real word, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:36.64,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I'm afriad I can't let you go
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:38.82,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What?!? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:47.32,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Sending all of you could upset the balance of this alternate world. Creating havoc that would make it impossible for Twilight to get the crown back from Sunset Shimmer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:50.64,Celestia,,0,0,0,,This is something Princess Twilight must do alone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:09:03.35,Luna,,0,0,0,,Time is of the essence. On the third day, when the moon reaches its peak in the night sky, the gateway will close, and once it does, it will be another thirty moons before you will be able to use it to return
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:20.00,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Spike, NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:32.24,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:39.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike! You're not supposed to... Spike? Are you a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:46.97,Spike,,0,0,0,,I... think so. But... I have no idea what you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:09.79,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight, you have to get it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:16.11,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What... does the rest of me look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:21.19,Spike,,0,0,0,,Um, like you. Only not you. Your muzzle's really small!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:22.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My muzzle?!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:26.58,Spike,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna scream again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:32.63,Spike,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.37,0:10:38.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't know. But that must serve as the gateway back to Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:42.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We need to find my crown as soon as possible and get back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:47.71,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I suggest we start searching the castle first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.19,Spike,,0,0,0,,Works for me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:11:01.67,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't think that's how the new you is supposed to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:17.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Come on, Spike. I do not wanna be like this for longer than I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:22.46,Spike,,0,0,0,,Look on the bright side. You don't have those pesky wings to worry about anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:37.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My magic! It isn't working!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:40.07,Spike,,0,0,0,,Makes sense. You don't exactly have your horn
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:41.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:43.82,Spike,,0,0,0,,We really need to find you a mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:58.43,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Spike? Are these artifacts she's stolen from Equestria?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:02.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:23.47,FlashSentry,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:34.30,Spike,,0,0,0,,I don't think this is a castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:40.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've never seen a place
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:42.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That's quite like this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:44.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Everything is turning 'round
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:46.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This crazy world is upside-down
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:48.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Getting on my feet
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:50.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's the hand that I was dealt
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:52.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But I don't have much time with them
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:54.37,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Got to learn all that I can
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:05.39,Twilight,,0,0,0,,They don't use any magic, or fly with any wings
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:09.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't get these funny clothes, skinny legs or tiny nose
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:12.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Everything's confusing when it seems so new
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:17.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But I look a little closer and it starts to feel familiar too
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:25.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What a strange new world
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:33.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to make heads or tails of this strange new world
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:42.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sorting through the small details of a strange new world
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:46.22,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What a strange new world
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:56.48,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:59.80,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I just found it, and I thought I should give it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:02.33,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you had dropped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:07.13,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Well, I did! And I was about to get it before you swooped in and ruined everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:10.00,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't pick up things that don't belong to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:12.31,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It... doesn't really belong to you, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:13.60,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:15.87,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,N-n-nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:19.57,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought. It's as good as mine and you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:23.91,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You really are pathetic. It's no wonder your best friends are all stray animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:26.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,How dare you speak to her that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.48,0:14:29.69,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:33.41,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I said - how dare you speak to her that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:38.90,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,You must be new here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:42.86,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I can speak to anyone any way I want
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:48.93,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you did that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:50.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I couldn't just stand there
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:55.52,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just that nobody ever stands up to Sunset Shimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:56.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sunset Shimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:14:59.98,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You've heard of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:01.37,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:06.95,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I don't think I've seen you around before. Did you just transfer to Canterlot High from another school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:12.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yes! Another... school! My name's Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:16.19,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm... Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sorry, what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.09,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It's Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:24.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It sounds like you're saying Fluttershy, but how can that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:29.56,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh my goodness! Who's this sweet little guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.81,0:15:32.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That's Spike! My... dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:38.24,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,He's so cute! Go on, eat up, little pup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:46.52,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you just give anything to know what they're really thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:48.33,Twilight,,0,0,0,,He usually just tells me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:50.52,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:55.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Nothing! Never mind
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:16:01.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sunset Shimmer said you picked something up. Something that belonged to her. It wasn't a crown, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:03.83,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:06.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Uh, lucky guess? Do you still have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:10.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But you know what happened to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:16.26,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,This morning, I was passing out flyers for the animal shelter like I do every Wednesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:22.32,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Canterlot's animal shelter needs more volunteers. Won't you help an animal that can't help itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:38.15,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I have no idea how it got there. But I didn't want anything to happen to it, so I decided to give it to Principal Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:42.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Principal Celestia? She's the ruler here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:48.94,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You could say that. Technically, I guess she and Vice Principal Luna do make the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:50.01,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Where is she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:51.33,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Probably in her office.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:55.66,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Third door on your left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:57.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:17:01.68,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh wait! You're not really supposed to have pets on school grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:05.80,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Might wanna tuck him into your backpack. That's what I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:12.02,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,They just get so lonely when I'm in school all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:15.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:17.12,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh no! I'm late for class!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:27.67,Celestia,,0,0,0,,How may I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:45.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My name's Twilight Sparkle. I'm new here, and... well, I understand that Fluttershy found a crown this morning and gave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:49.61,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Yes. I've had Vice Principal Luna put it somewhere for safekeeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:52.13,Celestia,,0,0,0,,No idea how it ended up in the front lawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:56.38,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Were you interested in running for Princess of the Fall Formal this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:18:03.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Uh, no. Not exactly. The truth is... Well, the truth is I... You see, the crown is actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:05.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess of the Fall Formal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:07.85,Celestia,,0,0,0,,It's Canterlot High's big fall dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:09.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Like the Grand Galloping Gala!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:12.05,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Uh, Grand Galloping Gala?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:16.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was a... big deal at my old school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:18.99,Celestia,,0,0,0,,And was there a princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:21.39,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yes, but she wasn't exactly a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:27.84,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Here at Canterlot High, the students select one of their peers to represent them. She receives a crown at the Fall Formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:33.98,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You asked me if I was interested in running for Princess. Can anyone run?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:40.03,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Yes, you just need to let the head of the Fall Formal planning comittee know you'd like to be on the ballot. Was there anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:42.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Um, nope! That was it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:45.89,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Well, if you do need anything else, my door is always open.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:51.88,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight, why didn't you just tell her the crown was yours and ask for it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:59.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was going to, but imagine if one of them showed up in Equestria saying they came from a place filled with tall bushy two-legged creatures with these?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:02.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We'd think they were crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:05.59,Spike,,0,0,0,,You make a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.59,0:19:10.50,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Looks like if I want my crown back, I'll have to become Princess of the Canterlot High Fall Formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:12.88,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So that's what I'm gonna do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:16.94,Spike,,0,0,0,,And how exactly do you plan on doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:18.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:38.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I know we’ve just met, but I was wondering if you might be able to help me with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:39.16,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:44.71,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I’ve decided to run for Princess of the Fall Formal, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:53.14,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, gosh! Sorry. It’s just, oh, running for Fall Formal Princess is a REALLY bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:54.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:20:00.06,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Sunset Shimmer wants to be Fall Formal Princess, and when she wants something, she gets it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:07.82,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,She’ll make life awful for anyone who stands in her way. Just ask the girl that ran against her for Princess of the Spring Fling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:09.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I have to try!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:25.14,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don’t think you understand. You’d have to convince everyone here to vote for you instead of her: the athletes, the fashionistas, the dramas, the eco kids, the techies, the rockers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:32.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why is everypony… uhh, everybody, separated this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:44.11,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was different at your old school, but at C.H.S., everybody sticks to their own kind. One thing that they do have in common, is that they know Sunset Shimmer is going to rule the school until we graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:46.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Not if I can help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:56.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So, ah, where would I find the head of the party planning committee?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:02.22,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy said she’d probably be in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:06.41,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:17.98,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Hi, my name’s Twilight Sparkle and…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:19.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:24.27,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Huh, are you psychic?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.29,0:21:28.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Uh, no. I don’t think so, unless of course that’s something you can do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:30.44,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Eh, not usually.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:36.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy said this is where I would find the head of the Fall Formal planning committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.24,0:21:42.26,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, huh? Don’t let the whole shy thing fool you. She can be a real meanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.62,0:21:44.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You two aren’t friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.31,0:21:48.26,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Waited a bit to get your name on the ballot, huh? Dance is the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.46,0:21:49.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I’m brand new here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.89,0:21:53.86,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oooh! I thought you didn’t look familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:22:02.33,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Though, now that I really look at you, do you have a twin sister who lives in the city who has a pet dog named Spike that looks just like that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:05.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Uh, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.43,0:22:11.71,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Thought so. Anywho, just need to fill this out you are officially up for the coveted Princess of the Fall Formal crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.60,0:22:33.46,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Wow! You have really bad handwriting. It’s like you’ve never held a pen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.31,0:22:36.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.42,0:22:39.28,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Somebody order a dozen cases of fizzy apple cider?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.91,0:22:43.20,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh, me, me, me, me, yeah, ha ha, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.23,0:22:46.59,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Can you bring in the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.02,0:22:47.98,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.46,0:22:53.07,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Hey, I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.25,0:22:54.37,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.61,0:22:58.41,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Sure, you’re the new girl who gave Sunset Shimmer the what for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.99,0:23:04.59,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Twilight Sparkle here is going to run against Sunset Shimmer for the Princess of the Fall Formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.89,0:23:11.76,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I’d think twice about that. Oh, sure, she’ll probably approach you all friendly like.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.41,0:23:18.12,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Sure am looking forward to some friendly competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.46,0:23:20.18,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,That’s so good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.26,0:23:22.78,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But then, here comes the backstabbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.15,0:23:28.12,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,About the only girl in this school you can trust less than Sunset Shimmer is Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.62,0:23:29.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:33.92,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,She’s the captain of, like, every team at Canterlot High.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:40.33,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,She’s also the captain saying she’s going to do something for ya and turning around and not even bothering to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.33,0:23:44.09,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the advice Applejack, but this is something I really need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:45.59,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.31,0:23:48.94,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Hey, how do you know my name is Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.08,0:23:52.93,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Um, I uh… didn’t you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.27,0:23:54.57,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.25,0:23:58.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, it sure was nice meeting you both. I’m sure I’ll be seeing you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.05,0:24:04.79,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,That one’s trying to hide a secret, but I am totally on to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:07.62,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,She’s psychic!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.10,0:24:10.35,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.78,0:24:14.02,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,This looks terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.15,0:24:18.29,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,There should be more streamers near the stage and fewer balloons.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.70,0:24:22.01,Snips,,0,0,0,,Yeah, streamers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.61,0:24:24.23,Snails,,0,0,0,,And fewer balloons.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.43,0:24:30.92,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Fizzy apple cider? Ugh! This is my coronation, not a hoedown.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.13,0:24:37.70,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, now, ain’t necessarily your coronation this time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.00,0:24:46.53,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so? You country folk really aren’t that bright. Must be why the other students say such awful things about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.81,0:24:53.70,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Obviously it’s going to be MY coronation. I’m running unopposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.99,0:24:56.85,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Not this time. The new girl just signed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.09,0:24:58.22,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.54,0:25:02.11,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I know, her handwriting is really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.98,0:25:05.57,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Where is this Twilight Sparkle?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.15,0:25:11.53,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to meeting the competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.72,0:25:27.27,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Can’t believe I didn’t recognize you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.55,0:25:34.89,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Should’ve known Princess Celestia would send her prized pupil here after my crown. And her little dog, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.15,0:25:36.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It’s my crown!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.21,0:25:44.37,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Whatever. This is just a minor setback for me. You don’t know the first thing about this place and I already rule it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.56,0:25:50.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If that’s so, why do you even need my crown? You went to an awful lot of trouble to switch it with the one that belongs here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.89,0:25:55.32,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Pop quiz: what happens when you bring an Element of Harmony into an alternate world?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.91,0:25:59.37,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,You don’t know? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.23,0:26:03.92,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,And you’re supposed to be Celestia’s star student?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.00,0:26:13.06,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Then again, what were the chances she’d find somepony as bright as me to take under her wing after I decided to leave Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.07,0:26:16.65,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Bit embarrassing that you were the best she could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.84,0:26:24.01,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I’d keep an eye on your mutt. I’d hate for him to be taken away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.47,0:26:25.96,Spike,,0,0,0,,Is that a threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.18,0:26:28.61,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.31,0:26:36.34,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,But I’d cut down on the chatter if I were you. Don’t want everyone to know you don’t belong here, now would you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.81,0:26:43.46,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,You want to be a Princess here? Please. You don’t know the first thing about fitting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.78,0:27:03.50,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I want you to follow her. Bring me something I can use just like I did with that last girl who thought she could challenge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.62,0:27:05.92,Snips,,0,0,0,,You got it, Sunset Shimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.65,0:27:12.92,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,When the crown and its power are mine, Twilight Sparkle will be sorry she ever set hoof into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.27,0:27:16.47,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Not that she would've been much safer if she'd stayed in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.39,0:27:19.98,Snips,,0,0,0,,Yeah, in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.26,0:27:22.55,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,What are you still doing here? Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.00,0:27:49.06,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.00,0:27:52.95,Trixie,,0,0,0,,The Great and Powerful Trixie
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.53,0:27:56.35,Trixie,,0,0,0,,needs some peanut butter crackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.38,0:28:00.84,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Voila!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.12,0:28:11.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sunset Shimmer is right. I don’t know the first thing about this place. If I'm gonna fit in and win votes, we need to do some research.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.21,0:28:13.06,Spike,,0,0,0,,Research?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.20,0:28:16.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This place has a school, I have to believe it’s got a...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.72,0:28:18.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,library!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.60,0:28:22.78,Snips,,0,0,0,,Got your phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.00,0:28:25.29,Snails,,0,0,0,,Got yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.07,0:28:44.33,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So, I just push the letters here and then the words and moving pictures come up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.09,0:28:49.73,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.65,0:28:54.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Maybe this place does have magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.65,0:29:04.82,BackgroundSong,,0,0,0,,When you’re a younger…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.48,0:29:07.81,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,Uh, girls, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.04,0:29:11.04,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,We’re just seeing how many hits our new music video has gotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.65,0:29:14.47,BackgroundSong,,0,0,0,,So the three of us will fight the fight…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.10,0:29:16.40,BackgroundSong,,0,0,0,,...there is nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.40,0:29:16.40,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,No. It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.36,0:29:21.25,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,No. The school computers are for research purposes only.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.07,0:29:30.26,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,It’s just as well, y'all. Some of the comments about our song were really awful: “Epic Fail,” “Funniest thing I’ve ever seen”!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.29,0:29:32.86,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Funniest thing they’ve ever seen, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.26,0:29:37.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Uh, I don’t know that that’s what you should take from…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.12,0:30:29.53,Celestia,,0,0,0,,The library will be closing in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.26,0:30:35.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I hadn't even thought about where we're going to sleep tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.56,0:30:38.13,Spike,,0,0,0,,Way ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.47,0:30:47.45,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's a little dusty. But it doesn't seem like anybody comes up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.22,0:30:50.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's perfect, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.38,0:30:57.26,Spike,,0,0,0,,So, how did your research go?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.26,0:31:05.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I found this book! It's called a yearbook. It seems to be something they use to keep a record of things that have happened at the school. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.32,0:31:12.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That's Pinkie Pie, Rainbow Dash, Applejack, Fluttershy, and I'm gonna bet the girl on the far right is Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.99,0:31:17.97,Spike,,0,0,0,,There's a Rarity here? I mean, uh... interesting photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.57,0:31:21.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's interesting because they look like they're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.63,0:31:25.39,Spike,,0,0,0,,They do look like our friends. But I thought we figured that out already.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.70,0:31:31.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No, I mean... they look like they're friends with each other. But it doesn't seem like they're friends now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.69,0:31:33.88,Spike,,0,0,0,,Not so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.20,0:31:38.02,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I just can't help but get the feeling that Sunset Shimmer had something to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.46,0:31:44.45,Spike,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't put it past her. But she wanted your crown 'cause she's planning on doing something even worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.45,0:31:51.21,Spike,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna stop her, you have to focus on making friends here. Can't worry about why these girls aren't friends anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.22,0:31:56.21,Spike,,0,0,0,,Even if they do remind you of your Ponyville friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.56,0:32:00.75,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You're right, Spike. Eye on the prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.23,0:32:11.11,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Good morning students, and happy Thursday. Just a reminder to pick up your ballots for the Princess of the Fall Formal today.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.29,0:32:22.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy said I'd need to win over  all those different groups if I want to become Princess of the Fall  Formal. So I've compiled a list of talking points.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.15,0:32:28.09,Spike,,0,0,0,,You made a list? That's so unlike you!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.44,0:32:33.48,Spike,,0,0,0,,Please! Continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.87,0:32:41.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'll start introducing myself. Sprinkle in some things I learned about their world into the conversation, show them how I fit in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.21,0:32:48.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Okay, Spike. Time to make a good first impression on my fellow students.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.59,0:32:53.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The whole world sort of depends on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.55,0:32:55.86,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.56,0:33:05.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why is everybody looking at me funny? Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.90,0:33:10.88,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What're you... Why did you...? Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.37,0:33:18.88,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.47,0:33:24.18,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. This is good! No one will recognize you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.53,0:33:25.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't I want to be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.63,0:33:31.83,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And we'll need a disguise for your dog, which is too bad. He really is so adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.97,0:33:35.51,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You know, with a little work, I think I could make it look like a rabbit, instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.51,0:33:37.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,A rabbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.41,0:33:39.64,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,There you are, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.33,0:33:41.81,Rarity,,0,0,0,,So much for the disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.95,0:33:43.79,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I've been lookin' all over for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.87,0:33:44.92,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.20,0:33:48.65,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Me three! I like your new look!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.91,0:33:52.59,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I do have an eye for these sorts of things. Not that you seem to care.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.66,0:33:53.61,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,WHAT?!?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.91,0:33:56.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why do you think she doesn't care?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.30,0:34:01.09,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No, never mind. Why were you all looking for me? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.42,0:34:04.37,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, she hasn't seen it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.45,0:34:05.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Seen what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.02,0:34:10.50,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's really not that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.67,0:34:15.80,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Twilight Sparkle wants to be your Fall Formal Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.07,0:34:22.50,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,What does it say about our school if we give someone like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.69,0:34:25.54,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,such an important honor?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.04,0:34:30.41,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Wha... I?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.43,0:34:33.13,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I take that back. It's pretty bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.55,0:34:41.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But this all happened yesterday! At the library! Has everyone in the school seen this? Is that why they were all looking at me that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.90,0:34:47.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do? No one is gonna vote for me after seeing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.97,0:34:51.50,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Not that it'll make any difference, but I'll still vote for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.50,0:34:56.80,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You were so nice to stand up for me when Sunset Shimmer was picking on me yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.25,0:35:00.37,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,If you still wanna run, maybe there's something I can do to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.62,0:35:05.55,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Word of advice: Don't accept her help. She doesn't take anything seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.68,0:35:08.25,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Why do you have to be so awful to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.84,0:35:13.33,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Don't play innocent, Pinkie Pie! You are no better than she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.42,0:35:16.26,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And WHAT is that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.11,0:35:19.91,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I am happy to offer up my assistance, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.93,0:35:23.23,Rarity,,0,0,0,,To someone who would APPRECIATE what I have to offer!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.90,0:35:33.05,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Listen to y'all carryin' on! Get over it and move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.93,0:35:37.49,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You mean like how you've gotten over what happened with Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.90,0:35:41.15,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,She said she'd get the softball team to make an appearance at my bake sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.15,0:35:47.52,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I tell everybody they're comin', and then not one of them shows up! She made a liar outta me! That's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.62,0:35:48.79,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Is not!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.82,0:35:49.95,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Is too!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.48,0:36:02.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Stop! All of you! I wanna show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.63,0:36:04.34,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You were friends once.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.09,0:36:09.23,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,The Freshman Fair. Y'all remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.59,0:36:10.52,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.58,0:36:13.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But something happened. I think that something was Sunset Shimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.65,0:36:19.27,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well it's a nice theory, darling, but Sunset Shimmer had nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.27,0:36:24.84,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,She's right. Sunset Shimmer isn't the one who ruined my silent auction for the animal shelter by bringing fireworks and noisemakers!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.71,0:36:30.88,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It was supposed to be a serious event, but Pinkie Pie ruined it!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.88,0:36:37.09,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? I got a text from you saying that you didn't want a silent auction, you wanted a big party!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.19,0:36:39.86,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Uh! I never sent you a text!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.21,0:36:41.29,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.33,0:36:43.82,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You don't think she's the one who's been sending  me those e-mails, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.82,0:36:50.69,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Every time I volunteer to help with the decorations at a school function, I get an e-mail from Pinkie Pie saying she has plenty of volunteers!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.69,0:36:53.63,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And then I find out she's done everything herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.83,0:36:56.26,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I never sent you any e-mails!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.98,0:37:00.67,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's the reason Rainbow Dash didn't show up for my bake sale!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.78,0:37:03.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Didn't you ever ask Rainbow Dash why she didn't show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.55,0:37:07.87,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Heh, I guess I kinda stopped talking to her at all after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.32,0:37:10.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Maybe now would be a good time to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.18,0:37:23.16,Rarity,,0,0,0,,They're actually talking! That's a good sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.69,0:37:31.23,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hugs! Ooh, hugs are always good!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.49,0:37:38.24,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Somebody, and I think we can all guess who, told Rainbow Dash that my bake sale had been moved to a different day
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.25,0:37:42.06,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Dash showed up with all the softball team and thought I'd cancelled on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.06,0:37:46.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So you're looking to dethrone Sunset Shimmer and become Princess of the Fall Formal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.56,0:37:53.47,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Gotta say, I'd really love to see that happen. I'll totally help you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.51,0:37:56.95,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,All you gotta do is beat me in a game of one-on-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.23,0:37:58.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.56,0:38:00.34,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,First to five goals wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.38,0:38:03.37,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,One-zip!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.51,0:38:59.21,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's game!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.81,0:39:04.62,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I... really thought you were gonna... pull it off there in the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.89,0:39:10.74,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So what's the plan? How can I help you be princess instead of Sunset Shimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.97,0:39:15.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But...  I... lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.10,0:39:20.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Of course you lost. I'm awesome! But I'm not going to help just anyone to try and beat Sunset Shimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.11,0:39:27.08,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,The Fall Formal Princess should be someone with heart and determination. You've proved that you've got 'em both!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.80,0:39:45.11,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And... could I get mine with extra oats?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.31,0:39:46.58,MrsCake,,0,0,0,,Oats?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.17,0:39:50.71,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Uh, scratch that. However you normally make it is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.09,0:40:02.64,FlashSentry,,0,0,0,,Oh! We've got to stop bumping into each other like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.42,0:40:14.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You know me! Always trying to make a big splash around here. 'Cause my drink kinda splashed... on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.43,0:40:20.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go over there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.25,0:40:29.34,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Don't even think about it! You're already trying to get a crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.48,0:40:33.25,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Who knows what Sunset Shimmer would do if you ended up getting her ex-boyfriend too?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.61,0:40:38.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to, I don't even know... We just accidentally... Ex-boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.89,0:40:44.94,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Flash Sentry broke up with her a few weeks ago. I can't believe she hasn't done something awful to him yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.61,0:40:53.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's just waiting until she has the power to do something really awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.33,0:41:00.26,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,All right, girls. Dance is tomorrow night and we still don't know how we're gonna get Twilight the vote she needs to be named princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.34,0:41:06.98,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Right now, folks only know the Twilight from the videos Sunset Shimmer posted online. We need to help them see her differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.81,0:41:11.12,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'VE GOT IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.29,0:41:24.77,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I mean, um, perhaps I have a solution. Now this may be an absolutely preposterous idea, but what if we all wore these as a sign of unity?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.94,0:41:32.43,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Freshman year, they were very, very popular. A way for everybody to show their school spirit! You know? "Go, Canterlot Wondercolts!"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.95,0:41:35.89,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I haven't sold any in ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.11,0:41:41.76,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I mean, the five of us are obviously very different, but deep down, we're all Canterlot Wondercolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.49,0:41:49.18,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Sunset Shimmer is the one who divided us, Twilight Sparkle is the one who united us. And we're gonna let everyone know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.83,0:41:52.36,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.76,0:42:53.68,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.49,0:42:56.05,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,We've got something to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.70,0:42:58.77,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,We may seem as different
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.49,0:43:01.03,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,As the night is from day.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.88,0:43:03.31,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,But you look a little deeper
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.24,0:43:05.32,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,And you will see
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.71,0:43:07.74,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,That I'm just like you
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.20,0:43:10.23,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,And you're just like me
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.01,0:43:17.86,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.40,0:43:19.44,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,We're here to shout
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.72,0:43:21.54,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,That the magic of friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.98,0:43:23.70,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Is what it's all about!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.91,0:43:28.08,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,We thought we're different as the night is from the day
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.40,0:43:32.31,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Until Twilight Sparkle helped to see another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.43,0:43:34.30,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,So get up, get down
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.92,0:43:36.52,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,If your gonna come around
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.99,0:43:38.70,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,We can work together
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.08,0:43:40.84,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Helping Twilight win the crown
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.08,0:43:42.96,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,So get up, get down
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.47,0:43:45.13,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Cause it's gonna make a sound
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.59,0:43:47.21,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,If we work together
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.72,0:43:50.33,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Helping Twilight Sparkle win the crown
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.33,0:43:52.10,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hands up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.48,0:43:54.23,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We're sending a message to the crowd!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.45,0:43:56.51,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hands way up, then come down,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.61,0:43:58.61,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We party together all around!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.73,0:44:00.68,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Generous, honesty
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.88,0:44:02.76,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Laughter, Kindness, Loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.24,0:44:04.98,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Twilight helped us each to see
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.27,0:44:06.69,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,All that we can be
