Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.74,0:44:19.34,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,cause it's gonna make a sound
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.82,0:44:21.57,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,If we work together
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.06,0:44:24.19,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Helping Twilight Sparkle win the crown
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.74,0:44:26.41,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.74,0:44:28.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No matter what I do
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.30,0:44:30.78,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And if we're different, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.25,0:44:33.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I wanta be true to you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.59,0:44:34.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If you follow me,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.38,0:44:37.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We'll put our differences aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.75,0:44:38.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We'll stick together
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.03,0:44:41.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And start working on that school pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.49,0:44:45.11,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Jump up make a sound
