Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.87,0:45:35.47,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Take those off! I have something I need you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.79,0:45:50.60,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Doesn't everyone look just fabulous?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.94,0:45:52.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It was a great idea, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.57,0:45:59.70,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Don't know what she's smilin' about. Twilight's the one that's gonna be princess of the Fall Formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.67,0:46:10.23,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Vice-Principal Luna! Something terrible has happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.23,0:46:24.25,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Isn't this just awful? And after Pinkie Pie worked so hard to make things so perfect! Why would Twilight Sparkle do something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.26,0:46:27.38,Luna,,0,0,0,,Why would you think Twilight was responsible for something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.59,0:46:29.36,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Because I have proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.68,0:46:37.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But... I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.33,0:46:41.46,Luna,,0,0,0,,This is clearly you in the photographs, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.92,0:46:47.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.03,0:46:53.81,Luna,,0,0,0,,I think it should be fairly obvious that the school cannot let someone who would do something like this compete for the Fall Formal crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.74,0:47:04.05,FlashSentry,,0,0,0,,Vice-Principal Luna. I found these in the trash can in the library. Thought you should see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.27,0:47:10.20,FlashSentry,,0,0,0,,Someone obviously combined these photos to make it look like Twilight was the one who trashed the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.27,0:47:13.20,Luna,,0,0,0,,I appreciate you bringing these to my attention, Flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.12,0:47:20.75,Luna,,0,0,0,,In light of this new evidence, you may of course continue your bid to be crowned the princess of the Fall Formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.88,0:47:24.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Thank you! You have no idea how important this is to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.73,0:47:32.10,FlashSentry,,0,0,0,,What was I gonna do? Not prove your innocence? Wouldn't be much of a Canterlot Wondercolt, would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.10,0:47:37.69,Luna,,0,0,0,,I am afraid enough damage has been done to the gym that we will have to postpone the dance until tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.31,0:47:42.66,Luna,,0,0,0,,If you will excuse me, I need to let my sister know about this latest development.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.14,0:47:51.36,FlashSentry,,0,0,0,,So, uh, I was wondering. If you aren't already going with somebody, wanna go to the Fall Formal with me tomorrow night?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.46,0:48:01.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That would be... Tomorrow night!? No, no no no no no, no no no no no! Nonononono! I can't! The portal! That'll be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.21,0:48:04.88,FlashSentry,,0,0,0,,One "no" would have been fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.74,0:48:17.07,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Everything okay in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.21,0:48:18.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.84,0:48:25.93,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Only it's not okay. It's not okay at all! If I don't get my crown tonight, I won't be able to go back to Equestria for another thirty moons!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.35,0:48:28.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, what are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.83,0:48:37.70,Spike,,0,0,0,,We tell them the truth. Let them know what's really at stake if you don't get the crown tonight. They'll help us figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.83,0:48:42.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What if they won't? What if when they find out how different I really am...?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.09,0:48:47.69,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight, these girls rallied around you 'cause they saw what was in your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.69,0:48:52.56,Spike,,0,0,0,,They aren't going to feel any differently about you when they find out you're a pony princess in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.01,0:48:57.34,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you followed me here, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.34,0:49:01.48,Spike,,0,0,0,,Me too. Unless of course we get stuck here for another thirty moons.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.60,0:49:05.21,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.37,0:49:07.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The Fall Formal isn't happening tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.57,0:49:08.97,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.05,0:49:14.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It had to be postponed because Sunset Shimmer had Snips and Snails ruin all of Pinkie Pie's decorations.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.37,0:49:15.48,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.70,0:49:17.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The Fall Formal has to happen tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.30,0:49:19.02,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Wha--
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.64,0:49:25.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.91,0:49:39.54,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You're from an alternate world and you're a pony princess there and the crown actually has a magical element embedded in it that helps power up other magical elements and without it they don't work anymore, and you need them all to help protect your magical world, and if you don't get the crown tonight, you'll be stuck in this world and you won't be able to get back for like a really, really long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.87,0:49:47.26,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm pretty sure that isn't the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.51,0:49:49.36,Spike,,0,0,0,,Nope, she's pretty much spot-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.36,0:49:50.40,Rarity,,0,0,0,,He can talk!?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.88,0:49:57.75,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and back where I come from, I'm not even a dog! I'm a ferocious, fire-breathing dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.86,0:50:03.19,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,This is so amazing! Tell me, what are you thinking right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.54,0:50:09.11,Spike,,0,0,0,,Sure would love a scratch behind the old ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.14,0:50:12.14,Spike,,0,0,0,,Uh, maybe later.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.42,0:50:13.79,Twilight,,0,0,0,,How did you know all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.86,0:50:14.86,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Just a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.18,0:50:19.40,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! Let me get this straight. You're a pony?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.48,0:50:20.84,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You're a princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.66,0:50:23.46,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You're from another world?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.49,0:50:27.72,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That... is...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.72,0:50:30.06,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.75,0:50:34.13,Spike,,0,0,0,,See? Told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.74,0:50:40.82,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I simply cannot believe they did all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.82,0:50:45.70,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,If I only had some kind of party cannon that could decorate everything super fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.93,0:50:50.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I know it seems impossible, but, maybe if we all work together?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.54,0:50:56.95,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Now that's the kind of can do spirit I'm lookin' for in a Fall Formal princess! Let's do it, y'all!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.22,0:50:57.92,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.03,0:50:58.75,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Rock on!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.11,0:51:00.04,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeedily!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.06,0:51:04.93,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's time for us to come together
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.56,0:51:09.39,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's the only way that things will get better
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.01,0:51:11.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's time for us to take a stand
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.40,0:51:16.67,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So come on and lend a helping hand
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.54,0:51:20.25,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Fix it up
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.73,0:51:21.70,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's all right
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.68,0:51:25.41,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,We'll get it ready by tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.28,0:51:27.02,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Mix it up
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.82,0:51:28.83,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Yeah, help a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.41,0:51:32.75,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,We'll come together in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.88,0:51:40.63,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,It's time to show that we've got school spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.22,0:51:44.27,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Raise your voice and let everyone hear it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.77,0:51:47.48,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,It's time to show that we're strong
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.24,0:51:51.83,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,So come on, everybody, sing along
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.76,0:51:59.78,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Look how we've all come together
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.13,0:52:06.34,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Things are only just starting to get better
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.86,0:52:13.31,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Look how we've all come together
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.94,0:52:21.11,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Things are only gonna get better, better, better, better!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.05,0:52:24.66,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Fix it up, yeah, it's all right
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.38,0:52:28.36,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,We'll get it ready by tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.93,0:52:31.68,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Mix it up, yeah, help a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.04,0:52:35.09,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,We'll come together in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.89,0:52:38.34,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Fix it up, yeah, it's all right
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.25,0:52:42.01,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,We'll get it ready by tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.81,0:52:45.49,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Mix it up, yeah, help a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.19,0:52:49.68,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,We'll come together, together now!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.40,0:53:01.73,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,This... looks... sooooo... GOOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.97,0:53:07.55,Celestia,,0,0,0,,All right, everyone! Fall Formal is back on for this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.19,0:53:16.53,Celestia,,0,0,0,,So you'd better get out of here and start getting ready. Don't forget to cast your ballots for the Fall Formal Princess on your way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.79,0:53:18.17,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You got my vote, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.60,0:53:22.12,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Mine, too!\NMine, too!\NMine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.62,0:53:32.51,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,You're lucky she was able to pull this off. Next time I ask you to make a mess of things, try to show a little restraint!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.51,0:53:36.62,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I need this Formal to go on tonight just as much as she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.28,0:53:41.77,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I still can't believe we pulled that off!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.78,0:53:44.42,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I can! We're awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.52,0:53:49.87,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Enough chatter, girls. We need to get ready, and we need to look fabulous!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.87,0:53:52.57,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,This is our big night
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.81,0:53:56.56,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,We're getting ready and we're doing it up right
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.13,0:53:59.78,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,This is our big night
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.32,0:54:03.88,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Friendship's arrived now we'll start it out right
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.91,0:54:06.86,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,The time's right
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.96,0:55:04.64,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,PESNYA
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.46,0:55:21.80,FlashSentry,,0,0,0,,Uh, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.87,0:55:30.10,FlashSentry,,0,0,0,,Look, I know you said "no" about going to the Fall Formal with me, but would you reconsider and at least have one dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.21,0:55:42.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I didn't say "no"! I mean, I did, but... I didn't mean no, to you. I was, well, what I mean is... yes. I'd love to dance with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.82,0:56:07.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Anybody see Sunset Shimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.77,0:56:12.72,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Maybe she was too embarrassed to show! She's gotta know you won by a landslide!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.20,0:56:13.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.53,0:56:24.58,Celestia,,0,0,0,,First off, I want to say how wonderful everything looks tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.58,0:56:29.71,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You all did a magnificent job pulling things together after the unfortunate events of earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.02,0:56:36.40,Celestia,,0,0,0,,And now, without further ado, I'd like to announce the winner of this year's Fall Formal crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.75,0:56:42.74,Celestia,,0,0,0,,The Princess of this year's Fall Formal is...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.60,0:56:47.23,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Twilight Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.40,0:56:57.65,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.55,0:57:05.09,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight, HELP!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.09,0:57:06.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.84,0:57:11.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,They've got Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.69,0:57:35.03,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,That’s close enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.88,0:57:42.26,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.48,0:57:44.77,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Don’t hurt him!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.78,0:57:48.00,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Oh, I wouldn’t dream of it…I’m not a monster, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.32,0:57:49.26,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.55,0:58:02.50,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,You don’t belong here. Give me the crown, and you  can go back to Equestria tonight. Or keep it, and never go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.58,0:58:09.13,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Tick tock, Twilight, haven’t got all night. The  portal will be closing on its own in less than an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.72,0:58:13.11,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,So, what’s your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.64,0:58:18.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.35,0:58:24.91,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,What!? Equestria. Your friends. Lost to your forever. Don’t you see what I’m about to do to the portal?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.91,0:58:32.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I’ve also seen what you’ve been able to do here without magic. Equestria will find a way to survive without my Element of Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.89,0:58:42.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This place might not, if I allow it to fall into your hands. So go ahead, destroy the portal. You are not getting this crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.77,0:58:46.47,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Fine. You win.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.98,0:58:52.65,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You are so awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.65,0:58:55.20,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I can’t believe you were going to do that for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.28,0:58:58.09,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It’s no wonder you were a real live princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.00,0:59:02.63,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, she’s so very special.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.18,0:59:13.58,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Grab him you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.80,0:59:25.93,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Spike! Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.91,0:59:34.02,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.69,0:59:48.24,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I’ll take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.79,0:59:55.90,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,At last more power than I have ever imagined.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.71,1:00:48.97,Snips,,0,0,0,,This is going to be so cool!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.25,1:01:10.95,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I’ve had to jump through so many hoops tonight just to get my hands on this crown and it really should have been mine all along.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.55,1:01:23.59,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,But let’s let bygones be bygones. I am your princess now, and you will be loyal to me!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.47,1:01:45.09,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Round them up and bring them to the portal.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.61,1:01:57.89,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Spoiler alert: I was bluffing when I said I was going to destroy the portal. I don’t want to rule this pathetic little high school;
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.89,1:02:05.65,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I want Equestria! And with my own little teenage army behind me I am going to get it!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.60,1:02:10.78,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No, you’re not!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.59,1:02:20.47,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Oh, please! What exactly do you think you’re going to do to stop me? I have magic, and you have nothing!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.01,1:02:23.04,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,She has us!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.82,1:02:33.03,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Gee, the gang really is all back together again.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.40,1:02:44.52,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Now step aside! Twilight has tried to interfere with my plans one too many times already and she needs to be dealt with.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.59,1:02:52.03,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.01,1:03:06.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The magic contained in my Element was able to unite with those that helped create it
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.12,1:03:20.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Honesty
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.05,1:03:28.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Kindness
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.73,1:03:37.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.17,1:03:44.75,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Generosity
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.33,1:03:51.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Loyalty
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.41,1:03:55.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Magic
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.92,1:04:04.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Together with a crown they create a power beyond anything you could imagine and it is a power you don’t have the ability to control.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.83,1:04:12.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The crown may be upon your head, Sunset Shimmer, but you can not wield it, because you do not possess the most powerful magic of all:
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.60,1:04:14.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,the magic of friendship!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.94,1:04:26.22,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,No! What is happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.94,1:04:34.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Here and in Equestria, it is the only magic  that can truly unite us all.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.43,1:05:24.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You will never rule in Equestria. Any power you may have had in this world is gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.17,1:05:29.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Tonight, you have shown everyone who you really are. You’ve shown them what is in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.16,1:05:38.04,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Uh. I’m sorry. I’m so sorry. I didn’t know there was another way.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.07,1:05:49.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The magic of friendship doesn’t just exist in Equestria, it’s everywhere. You can seek it out. Or you can forever be alone. The choice is yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.81,1:05:57.47,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,But… but all I’ve ever done since being here is drive everyone else apart. I don’t know the first thing about friendship.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.10,1:06:02.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I bet they can teach you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.74,1:06:04.79,Spike,,0,0,0,,Those are my girls! Woohoo!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.79,1:06:07.53,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Did that dog just talk? Woah. Weird.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.98,1:06:12.40,Spike,,0,0,0,,Seriously? The talking dog is the weird thing about all this?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.40,1:06:15.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I, for one, think you’re adorable.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.27,1:06:16.55,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.79,1:06:28.99,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I believe this belongs to you. A true princess in any world leads, not by forcing others to bow before her, but by inspiring others to stand with her.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.99,1:06:37.47,Celestia,,0,0,0,,We have all seen that you are capable of just that. I hope you see it, too, Princess Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.42,1:06:40.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.40,1:06:47.83,FlashSentry,,0,0,0,,Would now be a completely awkward time to ask you for that dance?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.14,1:06:59.49,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,This is our big night
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.75,1:07:03.51,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,We made it happen, now let's party all night
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.30,1:07:09.20,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,We're here now and we worked so hard to make it come around
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.27,1:07:12.43,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,To tonight so let's try to make it last forever
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.85,1:07:16.40,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Cool lights so bright, beat is pumping through the night
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.61,1:07:19.86,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Party's starting, DJ's got the music just right!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.32,1:07:23.76,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Six friends on their way up now
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.64,1:07:33.39,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Six friends here to show you how
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.71,1:07:44.81,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,This is our big night
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.94,1:07:50.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You’ll look out for her, won’t you?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.95,1:07:56.31,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Of course, we will. Although I do expect some sort of apology for last spring’s debacle.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.31,1:07:59.75,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling she’ll be handing out a lot of apologies.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.11,1:08:04.30,Spike,,0,0,0,,We better get going.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.07,1:08:09.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I know we’ve only been friends for a short time, but I’m going to miss all of you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.60,1:08:19.33,Spike,,0,0,0,,That crown really does suit you, Princess Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.33,1:08:23.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You know what, Spike? I am starting to feel a little more comfortable wearing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.86,1:08:25.22,Spike,,0,0,0,,And the wings?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.22,1:08:33.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I’ve been walking on two legs and picking things up with these. Wings? I’m thrilled that’s all I’ll be dealing with back in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.48,1:08:48.34,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh, bummer!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.38,1:09:03.79,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.79,1:09:05.59,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Ah, you’re back!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.59,1:09:06.87,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You’ve got your crown!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.48,1:09:09.52,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I knew you could do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.52,1:09:11.43,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Oh, we were so worried.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.43,1:09:13.82,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Sunset Shimmer, is she alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.82,1:09:18.37,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I think she’s going to be fine. I left her in good hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.59,1:09:21.05,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What are hands?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.85,1:09:27.77,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Where did you stay?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.77,1:09:28.67,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What did they wear?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.67,1:09:29.64,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Did you have fun?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.64,1:09:30.49,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What’d you eat?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.49,1:09:32.47,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Was she just as awesome as me?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.17,1:09:38.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I want to tell you all everything, I do, but I’m just so exhausted from all the dancing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.14,1:09:39.29,FewPoniesSimultaneously,,0,0,0,,Dancing?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.67,1:09:45.04,FlashSentry,,0,0,0,,We’ve got to stop bumping into each other like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.00,1:09:49.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.23,1:09:56.16,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,He’s the new member of the castle guard, Flash Sentry, I think. Why? Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.16,1:09:57.57,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.94,1:10:01.72,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Oooh! Somepony’s got a crush on the new guy!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.72,1:10:03.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No. No I don’t.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.24,1:10:06.60,Rarity,,0,0,0,,She does! She absolutely does!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.60,1:10:09.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Don’t be ridiculous. I don’t even know him. He just…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.92,1:10:19.37,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Totally reminds you of a guy you met in the other world who played guitar, was in a band, and helped prove you didn't destroy all the decorations for a big dance, so you could still run for princess of the big dance, and then asked you to dance at that dance!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.41,1:10:20.60,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.54,1:10:23.01,Twilight,,0,0,0,,How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.55,1:10:24.81,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Just a hunch!
